{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"45c564cf0f","title":"清平乐·六盘山世","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5824f2d1d0","index":0,"year":1935,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"45c564cf0f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9106dfac83","type":"paragraph","text":"清平乐·六盘山世","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"8d262d5e6a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年10月）天高云淡，望断南飞雁。不到长城则非好汉，届指行程二万。六盘山上高峰，红旗漫卷西风。今日长续在手，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"add0bc6ff5","type":"paragraph","text":"何时缚住苍龙？H","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"e91d20a0f0","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]六盘山，在宁夏回族自治区南部固原县西南，是六盘山山脉的主峰，险窄的山路要盘旋多重才能到达峰顶。毛泽东在1935年9月中旬率领中央红军进入甘肃省南部，10月上旬，突破敌人的封锁线，打跨了敌人的骑兵部队，胜利地越过六盘山。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"40e0bdd5e7","type":"paragraph","text":"[21长城，借指长征的目的地。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"a819addbdd","type":"paragraph","text":"131红旗，首次发表时原作“施头”，1963年版《毛主席诗词》改为“红旗”。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"2083c39a99","type":"paragraph","text":"[4]今日长续在手，何时缚住苍龙？化用南宋刘克庄《贺新郎》词：“问长缓何时入手，缚将我主？”苍龙，是一种凶神恶煞。《后汉书·张纯传》注：","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"af4681b4a3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东自注：“苍龙：蒋介石，不是日本人。因为当前全副精神要对付的是蒋不是日。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"45c564cf0f"},{"id":"c02bdebf56","type":"paragraph","text":"天京汉线西元限行","index